<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Tsunoshima Co., Ltd.</title>

  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;600&family=Montserrat:wght@300;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1c66c3, #58a6d6);
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .center-content {
      max-width: 800px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 42px;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .en {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 18px;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      opacity: 0.8;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .message {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 2;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .contact {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .contact a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ffffff;
      padding-bottom: 3px;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
    }

    .contact a:hover {
      opacity: 0.7;
    }
  </style>

</head>
<body>

  <div class="center-content">
    <h1>株式会社角島</h1>
    <p class="en">Tsunoshima Co., Ltd.</p>

    <p class="message">
      美しい角島の魅力を未来へ。<br>
      もうすぐ始動。
    </p>

    <p class="contact">
      CONTACT<br>
      <a href="mailto:info@tsunoshima.co.jp">
        info@tsunoshima.co.jp
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
